sub_title: Managing Partner, Strategy and Innovation Director at SmartMoveX
summary:
ICT Business Professional and Expert with more than 25 years of experience in Product Marketing, Project Management and Business Intelligence to drive new products and services with customer-centric approach.

Passionate about technology, innovations and new business development.

Industry expertise across Urban Mobility, Smart City, Smart Urban Infrastructures, Internet of Things (IoT), Digital Transformation, Mobile & Internet services and User Experience Design.
